{
  "stem": "8569.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I mentioned before, we had to give away our furs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't remember the sequence exactly, but what happened was the-- the Jews were not allowed to be on the street after certain hours.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Jews were obliged to wear white armbands with a blue Star of David, Magen David, on the left arm.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very interesting because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the situation was awkward in terms of living.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jews couldn't-- they were fired from their position in non-Jewish or public offices.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- all there was is scramble to make a living.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's interesting that-- that there was the whole industry developed about the armbands.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother made us the white armbands, and she embroidered the light blue Magen David on it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there was a whole industry when people started to manufacture wholesale armbands made out of celluloid, if you know what celluloid was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Celluloid is precursor of plastic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Those were permanent in the sense that you can just wipe it off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You didn't have to wash them and iron them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were made out of paper in case you forgot yours, so you could buy it on the street made out of paper.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a whole industry about the armband.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To me, at that time I was then-- what? 12, 13.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a badge of honor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't recognize the intention of demeaning-- demeaning Jews as such.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't mind having it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was proud wearing it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But at that time, the movement between the Jewish and non-Jewish parts was still very free.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when I used to go with Isabela, I used to take it off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Simply because we are not allowed to go to the non-Jewish parts.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
